name: Querubi - The Initiator
description:
Music: Analog synthesizer recording.
Artwork: Mixed media using brush tip marker and digital animation - 2021 - gif - 452x640 - Aline Vieira @floresfeias - Part of Codex Crypto Angelus series.

Its tetramorphic form bears the four elements of alchemy initiation. Upon penetrating its astral cybersphere, the initiate's period of astral consciousness begins. He has visions and perceptions that go beyond ordinary beings. Your intuitions are keen, but your impressions are not always clear, especially in dreams; but behind it, the truth, it is up to the initiate to know how to interpret the code.
